# 🌦 Polytech Forecasting

**Polytech Forecasting** is a modern weather web application built with **HTML, CSS, and JavaScript**.  
It provides **real-time weather updates**, **7-day forecasts**, and **automatic location detection** using the **OpenWeather API**.

Live Demo 👉 [https://yourusername.github.io/polytech-forecasting/](https://yourusername.github.io/polytech-forecasting/)

---

## 🌍 Features

✅ **Search by City Name**  
Quickly find weather information for any city in the world.

✅ **Auto Location Detection**  
Uses your device’s GPS to automatically show weather in your current location.

✅ **7-Day Forecast**  
Displays a full week of weather predictions — temperature, humidity, and conditions.

✅ **Dynamic Backgrounds**  
The background changes depending on the weather (sunny, rainy, cloudy, etc.)

✅ **Local Storage Memory**  
Remembers your last searched city even after reloading.

✅ **Responsive Design**  
Works beautifully on both mobile and desktop.

---

